description: If you’re craving a delicious Southern BBQ experience, Fat Boys Cookin’ is exactly what you’re lookin’ for. They put care and quality into their juicy selection of smoked brisket, ribs, turkey legs, and sausages, and you can tell with every mouthwatering bite. Whether it’s your next meal or if you need the perfect trailer to cater your next big affair, Fat Boys Cookin’ is the best choice to book.
name: Fat Boys Cookin'
